// Quake 4 简体中文汉化项目 —— 语音字幕层（整块面板，Apex/HL2 风格）
// 由 q4game.dll 的 rvSubtitles 每帧驱动：
//   subBgY/subBgH/subBgA 面板位置/高度/透明度
//   subText0..3 / subTxtA0..3 / subRowY0..3 行文本/透明度/纵坐标
windowDef Desktop
{
	rect	0,0,640,480
	visible	1
	nocursor	1
	menugui	0

	windowDef subPanel
	{
		rect	130,"gui::subBgY",380,"gui::subBgH"
		backcolor	0,0,0,0.55
		visible	1
	}
	windowDef subText0
	{
		rect	136,"gui::subRowY0",368,13
		font	"fonts/lowpixel"
		textscale	0.19
		textalign	0
		forecolor	0.95,0.95,0.95,"gui::subTxtA0"
		text	"gui::subText0"
		visible	1
	}
	windowDef subText1
	{
		rect	136,"gui::subRowY1",368,13
		font	"fonts/lowpixel"
		textscale	0.19
		textalign	0
		forecolor	0.95,0.95,0.95,"gui::subTxtA1"
		text	"gui::subText1"
		visible	1
	}
	windowDef subText2
	{
		rect	136,"gui::subRowY2",368,13
		font	"fonts/lowpixel"
		textscale	0.19
		textalign	0
		forecolor	0.95,0.95,0.95,"gui::subTxtA2"
		text	"gui::subText2"
		visible	1
	}
	windowDef subText3
	{
		rect	136,"gui::subRowY3",368,13
		font	"fonts/lowpixel"
		textscale	0.19
		textalign	0
		forecolor	0.95,0.95,0.95,"gui::subTxtA3"
		text	"gui::subText3"
		visible	1
	}
}
